---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Breadcrumbs from '../components/Breadcrumbs.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Disclaimer - Nenamaga"
  description="Read our disclaimer regarding the use of educational materials and past papers on Nenamaga."
  canonical="/disclaimer"
>
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-8">
    <Breadcrumbs items={[{ label: 'Disclaimer', href: '/disclaimer' }]} />

    <article class="prose prose-lg max-w-none bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg p-8">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6">Disclaimer</h1>

      <div class="bg-amber-50 border-l-4 border-amber-500 p-6 mb-8">
        <p class="text-amber-900 font-semibold">
          Please read this disclaimer carefully before using Nenamaga.
        </p>
      </div>

      <section class="mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">Educational Purpose Only</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">
          Nenamaga is an educational resource platform designed to help students 
          prepare for examinations. All materials provided on this website are intended for 
          educational and reference purposes only.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">No Warranties</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-700 mb-4">
          The information and materials on this website are provided "as is" without any warranties, 
          express or implied. We make no representations or warranties regarding:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-slate-700 ml-4">
          <li>The accuracy, completeness, or reliability of the content</li>
          <li>The availability or uninterrupted access to the website</li>
          <li>The correction of errors or defects</li>
          <li>The absence of viruses or harmful components</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">Content Accuracy</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">
          While we strive to provide accurate and up-to-date past papers, we do not guarantee the 
          accuracy, completeness, or authenticity of any materials. Users should verify the accuracy 
          of papers before use in their studies.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">Copyright and Intellectual Property</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          We respect the intellectual property rights of others. The past papers and materials on 
          this website are collected from various sources and are believed to be in the public domain 
          or used with permission. If you believe any content infringes your copyright, please see 
          our <a href="/dmca" class="text-blue-800 hover:underline">DMCA Policy</a>.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">Limitation of Liability</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-700 mb-4">
          To the fullest extent permitted by law, Nenamaga shall not be liable for:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-slate-700 ml-4">
          <li>Any direct, indirect, incidental, or consequential damages</li>
          <li>Loss of data, profits, or opportunity</li>
          <li>Damages arising from the use or inability to use the website</li>
          <li>Errors or omissions in the content</li>
          <li>Actions taken based on the information provided</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">External Links</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">
          Our website may contain links to external websites for convenience. We do not endorse, 
          control, or assume responsibility for the content of third-party websites. Accessing 
          external links is at your own risk.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">PDF Downloads</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">
          PDF files are hosted on external platforms (such as Google Drive). We are not responsible 
          for the availability, security, or content of files hosted on third-party services.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">Not Official Examination Materials</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">
          This website is not affiliated with, endorsed by, or connected to any official educational 
          institutions, examination boards, or government agencies in Sri Lanka. The materials 
          provided are for study purposes only and should not be considered official examination 
          materials.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">User Responsibility</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-700 mb-4">
          By using this website, you agree that:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-slate-700 ml-4">
          <li>You will use the materials for personal educational purposes only</li>
          <li>You will not redistribute, sell, or commercially exploit the materials</li>
          <li>You are responsible for verifying the accuracy of information</li>
          <li>You accept all risks associated with using the website</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">Changes to Disclaimer</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">
          We reserve the right to modify this disclaimer at any time. Changes will be effective 
          immediately upon posting to the website. Your continued use of the website constitutes 
          acceptance of the updated disclaimer.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="bg-blue-50 rounded-lg p-6 border border-blue-200">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">Questions or Concerns</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-700 mb-4">
          If you have questions about this disclaimer, please contact us:
        </p>
        <p class="text-slate-700">
          Email: <a href="mailto:nenamagapapers@gmail.com" class="text-blue-800 hover:underline">nenamagapapers@gmail.com</a>
        </p>
      </section>
    </article>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  article a {
    color: #1e40af;
  }
  
  article a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }
</style>
